# 📋 Task Management Dashboard

## 📖 Overview
The **Task Management Dashboard** is a simple web application built with **HTML5, Tailwind CSS, and JavaScript**.  
It allows users to **create, edit, delete, and track tasks** efficiently in a clean and responsive UI.  
This project demonstrates **DOM manipulation, array & object management, and responsive design** using Tailwind CSS.

---

## 🚀 Features
- ✅ **Initial Sample Tasks** – Displays 5 predefined tasks on page load.
- ➕ **Add Task** – Add new tasks with a name and due date.
- ✏ **Edit Task** – Update the task name and due date.
- ❌ **Delete Task** – Remove tasks from the dashboard.
- ✔ **Mark Complete/Incomplete** – Toggle tasks with distinct styling for completed items.
- 🎨 **Responsive Design** – Works on desktop, tablet, and mobile screens using Tailwind CSS.

### 🔥 Additional Features (Optional)
- 🔍 **Filters** – View all / completed / pending tasks.
- 📅 **Sorting** – Sort tasks by due date.
- 💾 **Persistence** – LocalStorage support so tasks remain after refreshing.
- ✨ **Animations** – Smooth add/remove transitions.

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- **HTML5** – Page structure  
- **JavaScript (ES6)** – DOM manipulation & task logic  
- **Tailwind CSS** – Styling & responsive design  

---

